TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some informations.
Goodbye.
Me want to know about city areas.
What do you know of the plague?
I need infomation about places in Neverwinter.
Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
Text: 이상한 소문 같은 거 들은 적 있으세요?

TextEng: You know anything about the bad plague?
Text: 나쁜 역병, 뭐 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Me wants information about places in Neverwinter.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료제를 찾으려는 시도에 대해 뭘 아시나요?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> How has the plague affected the nobility?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Are you suggesting a revolt of some sort?
What are the different areas of the city?
Tell me about the Beggar's Nest.
Tell me about the Docks district.
Tell me about the Blacklake district.
Tell me about the Peninsula.
Where can I get equipment?
Where me get equipment?
Tell me about the City Core.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Certainly you can tell me.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can tell me. Why worries about me?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 너 말해 줄 수 있어. 왜 나 걱정해?

TextEng: Certainly you can tell me... we are <race> kin.
Text: 분명 말해주실 수 있겠죠... 우린 같은 <race> 혈족이잖아요.

TextEng: We both <race> kind. Why not tell me?
Text: 우리 둘 다 <race>야. 왜 말 안 해?

TextEng: You tells about City Core.
You tells about Beggar's Nest.
You tells about Docks district.
You tells about Blacklake.
You tells about Peninsula.
Can you tell me about other city districts?
Text: 다른 도시 지구들에 대해 물어봐도 될까요?

TextEng: Maybe tell about other city places?
Have you paid your safety tax?
You paid safety tax yet?
Yeah. I could kill you easy. Be safe. Pay me to go away.
Text: 그래요. 전 당신을 쉽게 죽일 수 있어요. 안전하게 지내고 싶으면 돈 내요.

TextEng: Yeah, me kill you easy, so you be safe and pay me not to.
Text: 그래, 나 너 쉽게 죽일 수 있어, 그러니 안전하게 나한테 돈 내.

TextEng: Uh, nothing. Back to my other questions.
Text: 아, 아무것도 아니에요. 다른 질문으로 돌아갈게요.

TextEng: That okay. Me just ask other questions.
Text: 괜찮아. 나 그냥 다른 질문 할게.

TextEng: I AM a guard, and guards stick together. Pay up or you are dead!
Text: 전 경비병이에요, 경비병끼리 뭉치죠. 돈 내거나 죽어요!

TextEng: Me is a guard! Nobody help you! You be dead or you pay now!
Text: 나 경비병이야! 아무도 안 도와줘! 너 죽거나 아니면 지금 돈 내!

TextEng: You are right, of course. I apologize.
You right. Me sorry.
